    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheese - The Cheese Collector</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Is a simple down to earth clicker game... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>a grindy clicker game. Compete against friends or the globe to have the most cheese. Unlock upgrades, choose a theme that fits you, View a user's profile and statistics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: Most of the features listed below will be added in later updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Leaderboard to see who has the most amount of cheese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Community and Non Community Created Cheeses to be put in-game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• An In game shop where you can use your click currency to buy items to advance your gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Funny Easter eggs and secrets that happen as you progress through the game with more being added over time.</p>",
